graph LR
    MMServing["ModelMesh Serving<br/>Operator"]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    MMServing -->|model registry &<br/>placement state| etcd["etcd v3.5.x<br/>(Required)"]
    MMServing -->|CRD types| KServeAPIs["KServe APIs v0.12.0<br/>(Required)"]
    MMServing -->|controller framework| ControllerRuntime["controller-runtime v0.16.3<br/>(Required)"]
    MMServing -->|manifest templating| Manifestival["manifestival v0.7.1<br/>(Required)"]
    MMServing -->|leader election| OperatorLib["operator-lib v0.10.0<br/>(Required)"]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    MMServing -.->|ServiceMonitor CRD| PrometheusOp["prometheus-operator v0.55.0<br/>(Optional)"]
    MMServing -.->|TLS certificates<br/>(non-OpenShift)| CertManager["cert-manager v1<br/>(Optional)"]

    %% Internal Platform Dependencies
    MMServing -->|InferenceService<br/>reconciliation| KServe["KServe<br/>(InferenceService v1beta1)"]
    MMServing -->|ClusterServingRuntime<br/>watch| KServeCluRT["KServe<br/>(ClusterServingRuntime v1alpha1)"]
    MMServing -->|REST auth proxy<br/>sidecar| OpenShiftOAuth["OpenShift OAuth"]
    MMServing -->|auto-provisioned<br/>TLS certs| OCPServingCerts["OpenShift<br/>Serving Certificates"]

    %% Integration Points (bidirectional / consumers)
    Dashboard["ODH Dashboard"] -->|UI management| MMServing
    ODHModelCtrl["ODH Model Controller"] -->|webhook interception<br/>on InferenceService| MMServing

    %% External Services
    MMServing -->|model storage<br/>HTTPS/443| S3["S3-Compatible Storage"]
    MMServing -->|model storage<br/>HTTPS/443| GCS["GCS Storage"]
    MMServing -->|model storage<br/>HTTPS/443| Azure["Azure Blob Storage"]
    MMServing -->|model storage<br/>HTTP(S)| HTTPSources["HTTP(S) Sources"]
    MMServing -->|CRD CRUD<br/>HTTPS/443| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API"]

    %% Styling
    style MMServing fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% Required external deps
    style etcd fill:#e87d3e,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style KServeAPIs fill:#e87d3e,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Manifestival fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OperatorLib fill:#999,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% Optional external deps
    style PrometheusOp fill:#bbb,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CertManager fill:#bbb,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% Internal RHOAI deps
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style KServeCluRT fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OpenShiftOAuth fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style OCPServingCerts fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style ODHModelCtrl fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff

    %% External services
    style S3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style GCS fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Azure fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style HTTPSources fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
